  <section id="doom-knight">
    <h2>Doom Knight</h2>
    <div class="images">
      <img src="images/doom_knight_sprite.png" alt="Doom Knight Classic Sprite">
      <img src="images/doom_knight_render.png" alt="Doom Knight D2R Render">
    </div>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Difficulty</th><th>Level</th><th>Health</th><th>Base Damage</th><th>Resistances</th><th>Abilities</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Normal</td><td>27–28</td><td>342–421</td><td>23–45</td><td>Cold 33%</td><td>Charge, fast movement</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Nightmare</td><td>61–62</td><td>1,252–1,354</td><td>52–76</td><td>Cold 50%, Fire 33%</td><td>Fast melee strikes</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Hell</td><td>89–90</td><td>7,100–7,800</td><td>85–124</td><td>Cold 75%, Fire 50%</td><td>Pack aggression, resistance to crowd control</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <h3>Lore</h3>
    <p>Doom Knights are undead warriors forged in the flames of the Burning Hells. Once noble champions, they now serve the Prime Evils as relentless enforcers of chaos.</p>
    <h3>Notable Drops</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Normal:</strong> War Swords, Gothic Shields, Runes (Ral–Tal)</li>
      <li><strong>Nightmare:</strong> Rare claymores, magic armor, runes (Ort–Sol)</li>
      <li><strong>Hell:</strong> Elite class swords, runes (Um–Gul), unique plate armor</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Affixes</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Prefix:</strong> Spectral – Increases resistances and phasing</li>
      <li><strong>Suffix:</strong> of Pain – Adds open wounds effect</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
<section id="abyss-knight">
  <h2>Abyss Knight</h2>
  <div class="images">
    <img src="images/abyss_knight_sprite.png" alt="Abyss Knight Classic Sprite">
    <img src="images/abyss_knight_render.png" alt="Abyss Knight D2R Render">
  </div>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Difficulty</th><th>Level</th><th>Health</th><th>Base Damage</th><th>Resistances</th><th>Abilities</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Normal</td><td>28–29</td><td>280–360</td><td>18–35</td><td>Fire 50%</td><td>Ranged elemental attacks</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Nightmare</td><td>62–63</td><td>1,140–1,270</td><td>44–66</td><td>Fire 75%, Lightning 33%</td><td>Fire bolt, elemental resist</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Hell</td><td>90–91</td><td>6,800–7,600</td><td>78–105</td><td>Fire 90%, Lightning 75%</td><td>Rapid-fire projectiles, pierce resistance</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <h3>Lore</h3>
  <p>Abyss Knights are corrupted archers of Hell, bound to spew dark energies in long-range volleys. Their elemental strength grows stronger the deeper into the abyss they reside.</p>
  <h3>Notable Drops</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Normal:</strong> Long Bows, Fire Arrows, Mana Potions</li>
    <li><strong>Nightmare:</strong> Magic crossbows, runes (Tal–Shael), jewels</li>
    <li><strong>Hell:</strong> Unique bows, runes (Um–Ist), crafted gear</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>Affixes</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Prefix:</strong> Cursed – Reduces player resistances</li>
    <li><strong>Suffix:</strong> of Blasting – Increases projectile fire rate</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="venom-lord">
  <h2>Venom Lord</h2>
  <div class="images">
    <img src="images/venom_lord_sprite.png" alt="Venom Lord Classic Sprite">
    <img src="images/venom_lord_render.png" alt="Venom Lord D2R Render">
  </div>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Difficulty</th><th>Level</th><th>Health</th><th>Base Damage</th><th>Resistances</th><th>Abilities</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Normal</td><td>29–30</td><td>480–560</td><td>28–55</td><td>Fire 50%</td><td>Fire Breath</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Nightmare</td><td>63–64</td><td>1,550–1,780</td><td>65–92</td><td>Fire 75%</td><td>Fireball Spread, Knockback</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Hell</td><td>91–92</td><td>8,000–9,200</td><td>105–135</td><td>Fire 90%</td><td>Fire Enchanted, Tanky</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <h3>Lore</h3>
  <p>Massive demons covered in molten scales, Venom Lords serve as commanders within the armies of Hell. Their blazing breath melts armor and will alike.</p>
  <h3>Notable Drops</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Normal:</strong> Scale mail, mana potions, low runes</li>
    <li><strong>Nightmare:</strong> Rare helms, magic belts, runes (Ral–Shael)</li>
    <li><strong>Hell:</strong> Unique armor, runes (Mal–Gul), elite polearms</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>Affixes</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Prefix:</strong> Burning – Adds fire nova</li>
    <li><strong>Suffix:</strong> of Hellfire – Fire splash on death</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="izual">
  <h2>Izual</h2>
  <div class="images">
    <img src="images/izual_sprite.png" alt="Izual Classic Sprite">
    <img src="images/izual_render.png" alt="Izual D2R Render">
  </div>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Difficulty</th><th>Level</th><th>Health</th><th>Base Damage</th><th>Resistances</th><th>Abilities</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Normal</td><td>30</td><td>2,000</td><td>42–68</td><td>Cold 75%</td><td>Cold aura, strong melee</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Nightmare</td><td>64</td><td>5,800</td><td>85–120</td><td>Cold 90%, Fire 33%</td><td>Slows enemies, high defense</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Hell</td><td>92</td><td>22,000</td><td>135–180</td><td>Cold 100%, Fire 50%</td><td>Slows, tank, aura enhanced</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <h3>Lore</h3>
  <p>Once an angel in the service of the High Heavens, Izual was corrupted and imprisoned in a demon form. Now, he haunts the Plains of Despair, a tragic reminder of Heaven’s fallibility.</p>
  <h3>Notable Drops</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Normal:</strong> Rare weapons, runes (Ral–Tal)</li>
    <li><strong>Nightmare:</strong> Unique maces, rare shields, runes (Sol–Io)</li>
    <li><strong>Hell:</strong> High runes (Um–Ist), unique body armor, elite weapons</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>Affixes</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Prefix:</strong> Possessed – Cannot be stunned</li>
    <li><strong>Suffix:</strong> of Frost – Adds cold damage and slows enemies</li>
  </ul>
</section>
